{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/364","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/364/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/364/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/364/events","html_url":"https://github.com/rspec/rspec-core/issues/364","id":860132,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU4NjAxMzI=","number":364,"title":"Mocking not initialized in around(:each) blocks.","user":{"login":"tylerhunt","id":6457,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY0NTc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6457?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt","html_url":"https://github.com/tylerhunt","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tylerhunt/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":true,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2011-05-06T19:15:29Z","updated_at":"2011-05-08T11:51:35Z","closed_at":"2011-05-08T11:51:35Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"The mocking framework appears to not be initialized properly before the example is run in an `around` block.\n\n```\nRSpec.configure do |config|\n  config.mock_with :rspec\nend\n\ndescribe 'around mocking' do\n  let!(:now) { Time.now }\n\n  around(:each) do |example|\n    Time.stub(:now).and_return(now)\n    example.run\n  end\n\n  specify { Time.now.should == now }\nend\n```\n\nThis results in the following failure:\n\n```\nRun filtered \nF\n\nFailures:\n\n  1) around mocking \n     Failure/Error: Time.stub(:now).and_return(now)\n     NoMethodError:\n       undefined method `stub' for Time:Class\n     # ./bug.rb:9\n\nFinished in 0.00039 seconds\n1 example, 1 failure\n```\n\nChanging the `around` to a `before` works as expected, and after `example.run` is called, the mocking methods are available inside the `around` block. It appears the source of the the bug is that `RSpec::Core::Example#run_before_each` is where the mocking framework is set up (`@example_group_instance.setup_mocks_for_rspec`), but `around` begins executing before this code is called. \n","closed_by":{"login":"dchelimsky","id":1075,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNzU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1075?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky","html_url":"https://github.com/dchelimsky","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":